title: Kuroneko to Koushaku no Juusha
sinopse:
After sneaking into the English viscount Crawford's mansion, the legendary burglar Cat Tail destroyed furniture with a value of more than 1.8 million yen. However, she is caught by the house's butler, Lucien Marquis...

Will this mark the start of a love story between a thief and a servant?

(Source: Amazon)
